&quot;I asked you to support how using the word &quot;jew&quot; as a verb is equivalent to Nazi behavior.&quot;  Wrong, dumbass.  Go back and show me where you asked me to use Jew as a verb and equate it to Nazi behavior.  Here is what you said:  &quot;I assume you have a plethora of arguments to back it up, persuading your audience on how use of the word &quot;Jew&quot; makes you a fascist, racist supremist.&quot;  Do you see the word &quot;verb&quot; anywhere in that quote?  Oh, but I suppose that I should know what you *intended*.  Maybe typing slower really would help you say what you mean more clearly, obviously it couldn't hurt.  <br>
